# HIG Doctor — Auto Review

When editing any file matched by this rule, **before finalizing the change**:

1. Read `.cursor/skills/hig-doctor/SKILL.md` and follow its review workflow.
2. Cross-reference the relevant reference doc from the index table (macos / ios_ipados / media-controls / foundations) based on the change's target platform and topic.
3. Surface any HIG violation as a comment or inline suggestion — do not silently skip.

Scope: layout · materials (Liquid Glass) · motion · gestures · controls · platform adaptation.  
Skip for: non-UI files, logic-only changes, test files.
